<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Privacy Policy | 1A Administration Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico">
    <style>
        body { background: #181824; color: #fff; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin-top: 3rem; }
        h1, h2 { color: #a084e8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar", { user, active }) %>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Discord user ID, username, and avatar (when you log in).</li>
            <li>Event and certification data you create or manage.</li>
            <li>Server and channel IDs for event posting.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and improve the Service.</li>
            <li>To manage events, certifications, and Discord integrations.</li>
            <li>To ensure security and prevent abuse.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties.</li>
            <li>Data may be shared with Discord as required for bot functionality.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
            We retain your data as long as necessary to provide the Service. You may request deletion of your data by contacting us.
        </p>
        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
            We use session cookies for authentication and security. No tracking or advertising cookies are used.
        </p>
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>You may request access to or deletion of your data at any time.</li>
            <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:main@xanderxx.xyz">main@xanderxx.xyz</a> for requests.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be posted on this page.
        </p>
        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>
            For questions, contact the server administrators or email: <a href="mailto:main@xanderxx.xyz">main@xanderxx.xyz</a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5"><a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Back to Home</a></p>
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>